      "B": "Opens on V7(C7), Gm7-C7 to I (Fmaj7), Em9-A13 tonicizing vi, chromatic Eb9#11, Dm7-G7-C7b9 ii-V chain resolving to I",
      "A2": "Repeat of A: I-vi-IV, subdominant minor, D7-G7 and ii-V (Gm7-C7) resolving to I with plagal Bb tag"
    },
